  "content": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"morningradio\">MorningRadio</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Designed to be a healthy \"first screen\" in the morning. News summaries, updates, and enough information about the latest events that you don't feel the need to endlessly doomscroll.</p>\n<p class=\"\">The goal was to repurpose the tik-tok style endless vertical scroll but instead fill it with interesting and useful websites, tools, and news articles (populated through my Pinboard bookmarks)</p>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_400/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1200/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 80vw, 100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>\n<p class=\"\">I even experimented (unsuccessfully) with creating a home screen widget.</p>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png\" alt=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_400/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1200/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 80vw, 100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>",
